  "title": "Forklift Truck Driver (West, Rigger & Signalman)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Maintain and operate material handling equipment, including forklifts and reach stackers.</li>\n  <li>Handle the loading and unloading of goods while ensuring safety, proper stacking, and secure transport.</li>\n  <li>Pick, pack, and distribute goods and assist in periodic stock-taking activities.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for documentation related to dispatch and delivery.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a <strong>valid forklift license</strong> and a <strong>Certificate in Rigger &amp; Signalman.</strong></li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience as a Forklift Driver with good knowledge of warehousing and logistics operations.</li>\n  <li>Basic computer skills for inventory and tracking purposes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
